text: Céline Sallette (born 25 April 1980) is a French actress. In 2012, she was nominated for the César Award for Most Promising Actress for her role in House of Tolerance. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:French movie actors Category:French television actors Category:French stage actors Category:French voice actors Category:Actors from Bordeaux
